# Cursor Rules used by the AI

## Project Context
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4
- Zustand for state management
- Framer Motion for animations
- Lucide React for icons

## Styling
- Use Tailwind v4 syntax.
- Use `glass` and `glass-dark` utilities for windows and panels.
- Follow macOS design language (rounded corners, blurred backgrounds, system fonts).

## Component Structure
- `src/components/desktop`: System level components (Desktop, Dock, MenuBar)
- `src/components/windows`: Window management and frames
- `src/components/apps`: Individual application content

## State Management
- Use Zustand for global state (window manager, active app, etc.)

